						<p>Door-post of the <hi rend="italic">gōpura</hi> of the same temple.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">No King: (Vīrarājēndra): No date: c. 1207-52 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records that the soldiers must protect the temple of Vīrachōḻa-īśvaramuḍaiyār, its <hi rend="italic">gōpuram</hi> and its premises. </p>						

